Rem ************************************
Rem *** Test Bouton AMOS Pro 2.0 ***
Rem ************************************

Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Flash Off
Curs Off
Cls 0

Rem --- ACTIVER LA SOURIS ---
Show On

Rem --- Définir les couleurs ---
Colour 1,$FFF
Colour 2,$F00

Rem --- Dessiner un bouton ---
Ink 2 : Bar 100,80 To 220,120
Ink 1 : Box 100,80 To 220,120
Pen 1 : Paper 2
Locate 14,11 : Print "CLIQUEZ ICI"

Do
   Rem --- Détecter le clic souris ---
   MX=X Mouse
   MY=Y Mouse
   MB=Mouse Key
   
   Rem --- Si clic dans la zone du bouton ---
   If MB=1
      If MX>=100 and MX<=220
         If MY>=80 and MY<=120
            Rem --- Action du bouton ---
            Pen 1 : Paper 0
            Locate 10,15
            Print "BOUTON CLIQUE !"
            Wait 50
            Locate 10,15
            Print "                "
         End If
      End If
   End If
   
   Wait Vbl
Loop